// swaggo global type overrides — loaded via `swag init --overridesFile .swaggo`.
// Teaches swaggo the real JSON wire shape of the values.* value objects. Each VO
// is a struct with unexported fields + a custom MarshalJSON, so swaggo's struct
// introspection emits an empty schema (Record<string, never> in schema.ts).
// These directives map each VO to the primitive/struct its MarshalJSON emits.
// NO runtime behaviour changes — MarshalJSON is untouched. See story 967.
//
// Keys are the module-relative package path swaggo resolves for each type
// (PkgPath = searchDir-relative import path, since the repo root has no Go
// files for `go list` to anchor the full module path). Scalar VOs -> swagger
// primitive type names (Go builtins like `int` are rejected by
// BuildCustomSchemaV3); object VOs -> exported wire mirror structs.
replace internal/shared/domain/values.Year integer
replace internal/shared/domain/values.Minutes integer
replace internal/shared/domain/values.VoteCount integer
replace internal/shared/domain/values.Score number
replace internal/shared/domain/values.MediaHash string
replace internal/shared/domain/values.TrailerKey string
replace internal/shared/domain/values.ContentRating string
replace internal/shared/domain/values.LangCode string
replace internal/shared/domain/values.LanguageTag string
replace internal/shared/domain/values.CountryCode string
replace internal/shared/domain/values.SeriesStatus string
//
// Object VOs -> exported wire mirror structs in swagger_wire.go (same package).
replace internal/shared/domain/values.Rating internal/shared/domain/values.RatingWire
replace internal/shared/domain/values.Title internal/shared/domain/values.TitleWire
replace internal/shared/domain/values.Tagline internal/shared/domain/values.TaglineWire
replace internal/shared/domain/values.NextEpisodeCanon internal/shared/domain/values.NextEpisodeCanonWire
